            Carboxy- and carbamoyltransferases
SYSNAME     carbamoyl-phosphate:3-hydroxymethylceph-3-em-4-carboxylate carbamoyltransferase
REACTION    carbamoyl phosphate + a 3-hydroxymethylceph-3-em-4-carboxylate = phosphate + a 3-carbamoyloxymethylcephem [RN:R04281]
